Tools:

 - emitResourceFromFile.sh
    takes one of the html files [head or tail] and emits it as a single string resource.
    does all the conversion etc.

 - escapeForBundle
    the real guts of the above script

 - extractStrings.sh
    extracts FSWF's out of source code..

 - genIndex.sh
    Rebuilds a resource bundle index.txt

 - testVars.sh
    Source (. ./testvars.sh) this script so you can debug the locale explorer.